          <span class="lang-en">2. Website Use</span><span class="lang-id">2. Penggunaan Situs Web</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span class="lang-en">You agree to use this website only for lawful purposes and in a manner that does not infringe the rights
          of others or restrict their use of the site. You may not attempt to gain unauthorised access to any
