        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mt-10 mb-4">
          <span class="lang-en">3. Disclaimer</span><span class="lang-id">3. Penyangkalan</span>
        </h2>
        <p>
          <span class="lang-en">The information provided on this website is for general informational purposes only. While we strive
